            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "All right, I'm done! I've fixed Grandma's clothes!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It went pretty well, considering I've never done it before. Now, time to try them on."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Okay then, let's start with this... And this one next..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Tadaa! How's that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yes, pretty impressive, if I do say so myself! Hehehe!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...Ahem. \"Don't worry, everyone. Just leave this request to me.\" I sound just like her!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I'm getting closer to Grandma every day! Hehe..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Strong, kind, stylish... Relied on and respected by everyone..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I really do want to be as great an alchemist as Grandma was..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...Yes. Perhaps wearing these clothes might help me take that next step closer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I feel so much stronger, with Grandma looking down on me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Then it's settled! It's time to get synthesizing. I have to be more like her...!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x2a6,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x45,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'm feeling it now! Time for me to see just how close I can get to Grandma's level!"
        },
        {
